name: TRANSMUTATIONS
description:
#springoBRjkt
This is the first art I put here. Result of a partnership with the visual artist @DONGUTO! SPRING TRANSMUTATION deals with the various opportunities we are having to give a new meaning to our existence and to the real meaning of human life in the cosmos!
WE ARE ALL ONE!

Art Description: Riding through the waves of Techno and experimental House Music, @originallerry's soundtrack gains new perspectives with its addition to @DonGuto's animations, which uses all its versatility to magically describe the current moment and the observed life transformations mainly during spring
